{
  "page": "Sellagoro's Shield",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:PPTitan_of_Braavos.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/de/PPTitan_of_Braavos.jpg/300px-PPTitan_of_Braavos.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"199\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/de/PPTitan_of_Braavos.jpg/450px-PPTitan_of_Braavos.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/de/PPTitan_of_Braavos.jpg/600px-PPTitan_of_Braavos.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:PPTitan_of_Braavos.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The <a href=\"/index.php/Titan_of_Braavos\" title=\"Titan of Braavos\">Titan of Braavos</a>, as depicted by Paolo Puggioni in <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i></div></div></div>\n<p><b>Sellagoro's Shield</b> is one of the outlying islands which protect the lagoon of <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a>. The island is located west of the <a href=\"/index.php/Drowned_Town\" title=\"Drowned Town\">Drowned Town</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Ragman%27s_Harbor\" title=\"Ragman&#39;s Harbor\">Ragman's Harbor</a>, and the northeastern tip of Sellagoro's Shield forms the left leg of the <a href=\"/index.php/Titan_of_Braavos\" title=\"Titan of Braavos\">Titan of Braavos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafbraavos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafbraavos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The stony ridges and steep slopes of Sellagoro's Shield are covered with <a href=\"/index.php/Soldier_pine\" title=\"Soldier pine\">soldier pines</a> and black spruce.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> The Braavosi do not cut down the trees, instead using them as windbreaks.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sellagoro%27s_Shield&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiafbraavos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiafbraavos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Braavos.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_6\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 6\">Chapter 6</a>, Arya I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_26\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 26\">Chapter